# SENTRY API key — to enable the AI features after cloning:
#
#   1. Paste your Anthropic API key on the line below (replace the placeholder).
#   2. (Recommended) rename this file to  apikey.txt  so it stays gitignored and
#      your key is never committed.  The tool reads either filename.
#   3. Re-run the scan — the console will show "AI-assisted".
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored. Only a line beginning with sk- is used.
# The whole tool works WITHOUT a key too (deterministic mode); the key only adds
# the AI confirmation pass and the AI-written investigation report.

PASTE_YOUR_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY_HERE
